Complete Workflow for Optimizing Vehicle Utilization
----------------------------------------------------

Here is a graph of the complete workflow for optimizing vehicle utilization in the Car Subscription Service, represented in the DOT language:
```rust
digraph {
  rankdir=LR;
  node [shape=rectangle];
  CustomerData -> PredictiveMaintenance;
  CustomerData -> CustomerBehaviorAnalysis;
  CustomerData -> VehicleUtilizationOptimization;
  PredictiveMaintenance -> MaintenanceScheduling;
  CustomerBehaviorAnalysis -> VehicleAssignment;
  VehicleUtilizationOptimization -> VehicleAssignment;
  MaintenanceScheduling -> VehicleMaintenance;
  VehicleAssignment -> CustomerExperience;
  VehicleMaintenance -> CustomerExperience;
}
```
The graph shows how customer data is used to drive predictive maintenance, customer behavior analysis, and vehicle utilization optimization algorithms. These algorithms then drive maintenance scheduling, vehicle assignment, and vehicle maintenance processes, which ultimately impact the customer experience.
